"Valid-License-Identifier: MIT\n"
"License-Text:\n"
"\n"
"MIT License\n"
"\n"
"Copyright (c) <year> <copyright holders>\n"
"\n"
"Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a\n"
